				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Why bother with finding out which Black Reaver is the right one? Just kill them all, maybe you get a Jade Reaver.  To kill the castle BRs the best way is to clear the southern corridor,  clear to the castle, then cast an eye facing the locked door. With a bit of luck it'll appear inside the castle, behind the door. Target the BR and single pull to the southern corridor. Kill the BRs and leave the finally popping Lord Ghiosk alone if you don't want to deal with that summoning mob.
<br />

<br />
Then, with the BRs and Lord Ghiosk out of the way, clear the northern corridor and proceed as described.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=428341" target="_blank" class="postlink">Blana Foflana</a>
<br />
