			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">When you are in the right place, and cast Scars of Sigil, the spell goes off, but hits nothing. I've been camping there a LOT since I found this guide and do this:
<br />

<br />
1) Kill off all static/wanderers around what would be called the right side of the building that has the reavers.
<br />

<br />
2) Stand right at where the bridge just starts to cross the water (where the reaver building would be forward and to your right).
<br />

<br />
3) type /pet attack a black reaver00
<br />

<br />
4) If pet goes "taunting master" or whatever it sez...back pet off
<br />

<br />
5) /assist pet...then cast Scars of Sigil
<br />

<br />
6) if it hits nothing, have pet attack "a black reaver01"..and repeat
<br />

<br />

<br />
 Mine usually hits on "a black reaver00" or "a black reaver04"...it hits, and the appears just ahead of you on the ground, running. I pull back a bit into the courtyard and then have pet engage.
<br />

<br />
 - Trilon<br />_________________<br />[65 Arch Convoker]  Trilon Airer
<br />
Veeshan</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
