<br />

<br />
Correct, but not all the time your bolt will land. Sometimes you have to shimmy around a bit to get a good path for your "bolt". Its like a dungon where you can sometimes see a mob, cast but the wall gobbles your blast.
<br />

<br />
NOte however if you target the reaver via the arch method you should always target the top reaver if it is up. The only time I have failed to do so is when Trilon got there before me and cleaned house.  <img src="images/smiles/icon_lol.gif" alt="Laughing out Loud" border="0" /> 
