			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">An interesting strategy.  It's also possible to get into the long hall that leads to the glass ramp up (behind reaver 1) without a key.  Levitating with summon mount off of the balcony that's to the right of the initial gate makes it possible to get onto the wall.  (Stand on the flag mount near the top of the wall).  Mobs walking the wall will not aggro until you make it onto the wall.
<br />

<br />
Once up there, you can fight all the way to the traditional Neh'Ashir fight room.  Mobs will aggro on a 65, but of course all of them ignore a pet that's pulling.<br />_________________<br /><img src="http://www.ballio.com/mageguide/sticksigeci.gif" border="0" />
<br />
Life as a Mage: <a href="http://www.ballio.com" target="_blank">http://www.ballio.com</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
